A lot of twists and deaths. I feel like: Star Wars The Last Jedi is a big f*** you to the Skywalker Saga and fans. Two stories Finn and Rose; Rey and Luke changed emotions from hype to dull. Scenes with jokes that were meant to be  serious. Too many references from the processors. A endless space battle of the century. Unnecessary characters such as Holdo\, Rose\, and DJ. The Last Jedi feels like a episode 9 movie. The movie was unbreathable\, confusing\, and annoying. P.S: Leia should of been the character to sacrifice herself on the cruiser.
